This solutionuse composer.


For install dependencies open console in current directory:


`
php composer.phar install 

`



For running tu 

`

php composer.phar tu
`




Run docker image manually

in Crafts/Php dir :
`
docker build -t phpcrafts .
docker run -dit --name crafts_app -p 8080:80 phpcrafts

docker stop crafts_app
docker rm crafts_app
`


http://localhost:8080 is enable